Modify the Template to Decode the Lots Category
修改模板以处理多码类别
Modify the Template to Decode the Lots Category
In the benchmark, there are several files in the lots category that DBR cannot detect all the QR codes.
在上述基准测试中，DBR无法检测到多码类别中的几个文件的所有QR码。
In the benchmark, there are several files in the lots category that DBR cannot detect all the QR codes.

The reason is that the QR codes are relatively small and the image has a large resolution (3024x4032) while in DBR's template, there is a <g1>ScaleDownThreshold</g1> parameter which is set to <g2>2300</g2> so that the image will be scaled down for a better decoding speed.
原因是这些图片中的QR码相对较小，图像分辨率较高（3024x4032），而在DBR的模板中，有一个<g1>ScaleDownThreshold</g1>参数，该参数设置为<g2>2300</g2>，图像会被缩小以获得更好的解码速度。

The reason is that the QR codes are relatively small and the image has a large resolution (3024x4032) while in DBR's template, there is a <g1>ScaleDownThreshold</g1> parameter which is set to <g2>2300</g2> so that the image will be scaled down for a better decoding speed.
If we set the <g1>ScaleDownThreshold</g1> to 99999, we can decode all the QR codes.
如果我们将<g1>ScaleDownThreshold</g1>设置为99999，所有二维码就都能被解出了。
If we set the <g1>ScaleDownThreshold</g1> to 99999, we can decode all the QR codes.
The accuracy for the lots category can increase from 60.48 to 100 using the modified template.
使用修改后的模板，多码类别的准确度可以从60.48提高到100。
The accuracy for the lots category can increase from 60.48 to 100 using the modified template.
